          {
            "name": "Dr. John Smith",
            "role": "Doctor",
            "description": "Dr. John Smith was born and raised in Minnesota. He received his degree from the University of Minnesota in 1990. He practiced in Minneapolis for ten years. Dr. Smith entered the Master'Degree program in at the University of Minnesota in 2000. Dr Smith enjoys spending time with his family, traveling, and exploring the wilderness of the Boundary Waters.",
            "imageUrl": "https://cdcssl.ibsrv.net/ibimg/smb/200x200_80/webmgr/1o/s/5/_SHARED/staff_1.jpg.webp?0179ff3475d44b26f95e529c2abcf3dd",
